<i>noun</i>: 동기, 動機 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>동기, 動機</dt><br>
<dd>the psychological feature that arouses an organism to action toward a desired goal; the reason for the action; that which gives purpose and direction to behavior</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: motive, need, motivation</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
